<template>
  <v-data-table

</template>

      return {

          {
            text: '번호',
            align: 'start',

            value: 'number',
          },
          { text: '재난발생일시', value: 'calday' },
          { text: '사용자ID', value: 'user_id' },
          { text: '재난종류', value: 'calType' },

        ],
        calamity_info: [
          {
            number: 1,

          {
            number: 2,

          }
          
          
        ],
      }
    },
  }
</script>
